    "special": "<p>You do not breathe and you cannot consume provisions, but a Plasmic Core will restore 2d6 Stamina up to 3 times per day. You cannot wear armor or use weapons, but you are always considered moderately armored (encumbrance applied as normal for you), and do +1 damage on Jolt spells.</p>",
